:T:<N><G:90><G><Z><M:09><EOL>
*
*:SECTION=FIVE_AXIS_LAST_RAPID_Z_MOVE_UP
*
*:SECTION=RAPID_FROM_TOOL_CHANGE_MILL
*
*:SECTION=RAPID_LEADIN_FROM_TOOL_CHANGE_MILL
*
*:SECTION=FIVE_AXIS_RAPID_FROM_T_CHANGE
