:SECTION=CALC_INIT_MCODES
*----------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*   M Code                M Group               M Modal                      *
*----------------------------------------------------------------------------*
:C: MC(M_STOP)         =  0  MG(M_STOP)         =  0  MM(M_STOP)         = NO
:C: MC(M_OPT_STOP)     =  1  MG(M_OPT_STOP)     =  0  MM(M_OPT_STOP)     = NO
